      <title>特朗普的加密项目正在购买价值数百万美元的利基代币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/trump-s-world-liberty-is-buying-niche-tokens-worth-millions-of-dollars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着人们猜测去中心化金融借贷平台即将投入运营，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 的加密项目 World Liberty Financial 似乎正在购买价值数百万美元的专用数字代币。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/trump-s-world-liberty-is-buying-niche-tokens-worth-millions-of-dollars</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 15:17:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
