      <title>财政部长称欧盟债券可能对荷兰债务构成威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/eu-bonds-could-be-a-threat-to-dutch-debt-treasury-chief-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰财政部负责人表示，如果指数提供商将欧盟债券重新归类为主权证券，则可能对荷兰债券构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-13/eu-bonds-could-be-a-threat-to-dutch-debt-treasury-chief-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗和俄罗斯制裁可能缓解供应过剩前景，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于地缘政治紧张局势不断升温，且对俄罗斯和伊朗实施制裁的可能性抵消了明年供应过剩的预测，油价上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-december-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:30:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股从纪录高位回落，标普指数表现挣扎：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克 100 指数本周第二次创下历史新高，但随后回吐涨幅，原因是博通公司 (Broadcom Inc.) 股价飙升，带动整个芯片技术板块上涨。美国国债下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 22:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
